      "Saudi Arabia has quietly become one of the most exciting places on earth to host an event. In just a few years, the Kingdom has moved from a market with limited entertainment infrastructure to a global stage hosting royal weddings, international summits, sell-out concerts at Maraya, and corporate galas that rival anything in Dubai, London, or Singapore. If you are planning an event here in 2026 — whether it is a 300-guest corporate conference in [Riyadh](/locations/riyadh) or an intimate luxury wedding in [AlUla](/locations/alula) — this guide is your complete roadmap.",
