      "### Riyadh — The Capital of Scale and Prestige",
      "[Riyadh](/locations/riyadh) is the beating heart of the Kingdom's event scene. It is where government summits, financial conferences, and the most prestigious [corporate galas](/services/corporate-events) happen. The KAFD Conference Center handles 3,000-plus delegates with built-in 4K LED walls, while the Ritz-Carlton's Najdi palace setting defines luxury. If your event needs gravitas, scale, or proximity to decision-makers, Riyadh is your city — just book early, especially during Riyadh Season (October–March).",
      "### Jeddah — Coastal Elegance and Cultural Warmth",
      "[Jeddah](/locations/jeddah) trades Riyadh's formality for Red Sea charm. It is the romantic capital for weddings, with waterfront venues and a famously cosmopolitan, hospitable culture. It is also a strong choice for trade events and product launches that benefit from a more relaxed, creative atmosphere. Humidity and sea breeze mean outdoor events need a weather plan — but few backdrops beat a sunset over the Corniche.",
      "### AlUla — The Most Spectacular Setting on Earth",
