    metaTitle: "Luxury Weddings in Saudi Arabia: Why It's the New Destination (2026)",
    metaDescription: "Why Saudi Arabia is the new global destination for luxury weddings — exclusive venues in AlUla and the Red Sea, designer décor, VIP guest experiences, and a complete 12-month wedding timeline.",
    title: "Why Saudi Arabia Is Becoming the New Global Destination for Luxury Weddings",
    excerpt: "From AlUla's ancient canyons to private Red Sea islands, discover why Saudi Arabia is the world's most exciting luxury wedding destination — plus exclusive venues, décor trends, and a 12-month planning timeline.",
    category: "Weddings",
    image: "/blog/luxury_weddings_saudi_destination.webp",
