      "## 1. Do Not Ignore the Linen",
      "Your tablecloth is the canvas for everything else. For formal corporate dinners, skip the basic poly-blends. Heavy-weight linen in crisp white or warm ivory looks clean and premium. Want to go the extra mile? Custom-embroidered napkins with the company logo or summit branding add a subtle, personalized touch without looking tacky.",
