      "Charger plates are the foundation of your place setting. Gold-rimmed chargers give off a celebratory, classic vibe, while matte black or marble chargers look sharp, modern, and executive. Choose one that matches the tone of your event.",
      "## 3. Keep Centerpieces Out of the Way",
      "There is nothing worse than trying to network through a giant bush of flowers. Keep your floral arrangements below 12 inches (so seated guests can see over them) or go dramatically tall (so they can see under them). Using local Saudi flora mixed with imported flowers also adds a beautiful regional touch.",
